{"about_the_game":"Hello! I'm a solo developer from Finland, and this is my game that I have been making for 3 years. Place it in your wishlist if you find it interesting :)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What is Shifter?</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683390/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1735413690\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683390/extras/WhatDoYouDoInIt.png?t=1735413690\" /><br><br>It's a rogue-lite game where you can shift the direction of gravity. It has unique boss fights, weapons, skills, enemies, and more! You have a microchip in your brain, which has been hacked in your sleep. In order to wake up, you must complete the challenge given by the hacker!<br><br>Things you can do:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Change gravity </li><li>Grappling hook </li><li>Fight in interesting ways </li><li>Use cool weapons </li><li>Throw exploding heads </li><li>Update your character's attributes </li><li>And die! </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Different weapons</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683390/extras/weaponsGifSteam.gif?t=1735413690\" /><br><br>The world is procedurally generated so you can go in any direction in this complex dream world..  You can also use a grappling hook to move around quickly and to kill enemies. There\u2019s all kinds of different weapons such as regular weapons, shields, bows, machine guns and also <strong>weapons that are alive</strong>, exploding heads etc.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bosses</h2><br>There are many boss fights and enemies that interact with gravity-shifting mechanics in the game in different ways, and <strong>strange enemies like giant arms and other limbs that attack from holes in the ground and try to kill you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683390/extras/bossGifSteam.gi